# Ingredients
* 1 tbsp extra virgin olive oil
* 2 tbsp sherry vinegar
* salt
* 1/2 slice whole wheat or multigrain bread, torn in quarters
* 1/2 green pepper, coarsely chopped
* 1 heirloom tomato, coarsely chopped

# Instructions
* 1. Put olive oil and sherry vinegar in personal size blender.
* 2. Add green pepper.
* 3. Add salt from salt shaker.
* 4. Add bread, and then tomato.
* 5. Optional: add more salt from shaker.
* 6. Blend until chunky and incorporated, ~ 15 seconds.
